In-Scope Features

User Authentication & Authorization

Secure login for administrators and authorized staff

Role-based access control

Donor Management

Donor registration and profile management

Maintain donor details such as blood group, contact information, and donation history

Track donor eligibility and last donation date

Blood Inventory Management

Real-time tracking of available blood units

Categorization by blood group and quantity

Monitoring of blood expiration dates

Blood Request Management

Allow hospitals or authorized users to request blood units

Approval and allocation of blood based on availability

Priority handling for emergency requests

Search & Reporting

Search blood availability by blood group

Generate basic reports on donors, inventory, and blood usage

Notification System

Notifications to donors for blood donation requests

Alerts for low stock levels and nearing expiration dates

Data Management & Security

Centralized database for storing all records

Secure handling of sensitive donor and patient-related data
